* East Tennessee Hall of Fame (1988)<ref>{{cite web|title=East Tennessee Hall of Fame|url=http://dollyparton.com/life-and-career/awards_milestones/east-tennessee-hall-of-fame/1030|website=dollyparton.com|date=October 12, 1988|access-date=April 8, 2016}}</ref>
